{"tha-ap467:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap467:0.2":"Salakusumiyavagga ","tha-ap467:0.3":"Sumanatalavantiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap467:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap467:1.2":"talavantamadasaham; ","tha-ap467:1.3":"Sumanehi paticchannam, ","tha-ap467:1.4":"dharayami mahayasam. ","tha-ap467:2.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap467:2.2":"talavantamadasaham; ","tha-ap467:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap467:2.4":"talavantassidam phalam. ","tha-ap467:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap467:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap467:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap467:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap467:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap467:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap467:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap467:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap467:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap467:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sumanatalavantiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap467:7.1":"Sumanatalavantiyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}